      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "The drake can exhale one of three condiments in a 60-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 16 saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 14 (4d6) damage and suffers the effect of the chosen condiment. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage and suffers no condition. The drake chooses one of the following options each time it uses this action:\n\nMustard Spray: On a failed save, the target is blinded until the end of its next turn.\nKetchup Blast: On a failed save, the target is restrained until the end of its next turn.\nRelish Mist: On a failed save, the target is poisoned until the end of its next turn."
